rows.label: tlk43300061_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I hear that a boy from Iyasaki has
established a direct trade route
to Avaritia.

rows.label: tlk43300061_02_msg0002
rows.name:
That's great news for us! Just great!
It means we'll finally be able to get
back home to Invidia.

rows.label: tlk43300061_02_msg0003
rows.name:
...On the other hand, my wife's made
some friends here in Iyasaki, and she's
been learning local cooking, too...

rows.label: tlk43300061_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Said she won't go back till she knows
them all, so I've just been watching the
boats go by... At least she's having fun.
